        html: "<h1>Robert Neborsky, M.D.'s Expert Insights on Alzheimer's Disease</h1>\nGrab a cup of coffee, or better yet oolong tea for this interesting conversation between Cerna Homecare CEO Nick Payzant and Robert Neborsky, MD focusing on Alzheimer's disease. <!--more-->\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/e0ymA_VHXDU\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n\nDr Neborsky is a Neuro Psychiatrist; he is trained in the underlying neurological and pharmacological basis of mental illness and organic mental disease. He shares his expert insights on:\n<ul>\n \t<li>Hallmarks of Alzheimer’s disease and other types of dementia.</li>\n \t<li>What actions to take when these symptoms show themselves</li>\n \t<li>Importance of accurate diagnosis</li>\n \t<li>Depression's link to cognitive decline</li>\n \t<li>Benefits of natural alternatives for prevention/treatment</li>\n \t<li>Promising strides in Alzheimer’s drugs</li>\n</ul>\n...and more!https://cernafranchising.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/nick-cerna.jpg",
