        image: "/assets/blog/blogimage70.webp",
        seoTitle:
            "“Creating Hope” Alzheimer’s Association, Orange County Annual Gala – March 1, 2014",
        seoDescription:
            "The Alzheimer’s Association Orange County invites the community to its annual “Creating Hope” gala event.",
        html: "<p>The Alzheimer’s Association of Orange County hosted its annual “Creating Hope” gala, bringing the community together in support of Alzheimer’s awareness and research.</p>\\n<p>This important event highlighted the ongoing need for support, education, and funding to improve the lives of those affected by Alzheimer’s disease.</p>",
