            "Care plan oversight and physician portals improve coordination and efficiency in patient care management.",
        html: "<p><img src=\"http://www.cernahealth.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-o-matic/cache/4f775_webinars2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"HEALTHCAREfirst Webinars\" width=\"260\" height=\"160\" class=\"alignLeft\" style=\"float: left;\" />HEALTHCARE<em>first</em> recently presented a webinar on June 16, 2011 about what <a href=\"http://www.healthcarefirst.com/homehealth/firsthomecare-overview.aspx\" title=\"home health\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">home health</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://www.healthcarefirst.com/hospice/firsthospice.aspx\" title=\"hospice\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hospice</a> agencies need to know about Care Plan Oversight &amp; Physician Portals.&nbsp; Attendees discovered how <a href=\"https://www.firstcpo.com/\" title=\"Physician Portals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Physician Portals</a> can better your business by learning more about:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What is Care Plan Oversight (CPO), including requirements and who does or does not qualify&nbsp; &nbsp; </li>\n<li>What are Physician Portals and why they are important to your business practice&nbsp; </li>\n<li>Types of Physician Portals and which would work best for your organization&nbsp; </li>\n<li>How Physician Portals play an integral part in Accountable Care Organizations&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please <a href=\"http://blog.healthcarefirst.com/Default.aspx?app=LeadgenDownload&amp;shortpath=docs%2FfirstCPO+National+Webinar.pdf\" title=\"click here\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">click here</a> for a .PDF copy of the presentation.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Please <a href=\"https://healthcarefirst.webex.com/healthcarefirst/lsr.php?AT=pb&amp;SP=EC&amp;rID=19343482&amp;rKey=18b6386642542844\" title=\"click here\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">click here</a> to view the webinar recording.</p>\n<p>For more information about Care Plan Oversight, or to learn more about HEALTHCARE<em>first&rsquo;s</em> Physician Portal, <a href=\"https://www.firstcpo.com/\" title=\"firstCPO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>first</em>CPO</a>, contact us today!</p>",
