            "Accountable Care Organizations are reshaping how home care services are delivered and coordinated.",
        html: "<p><a title=\"HEALTHCAREfirst\" href=\"http://www.healthcarefirst.com\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HEALTHCARE<em>first</em></a>, along with its telehealth partner, Continuity Health, presented a webinar on April 5, 2011 regarding <a title=\"Accountable Care Organizations\" href=\"http://www.healthcarefirst.com/homehealth/firstcpo-overview.aspx\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Accountable Care Organizations</a> and how they will reshape the future of homecare.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Please <a title=\"click here\" href=\"http://blog.healthcarefirst.com/Default.aspx?app=LeadgenDownload&amp;shortpath=docs%2FReshaping+the+future+of+Homecare+Accountable+Care+Organizations.pdf\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">click here</a> for a PDF copy of the presentation.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Please <a title=\"click here\" href=\"https://healthcarefirstevents.webex.com/healthcarefirstevents/lsr.php?AT=pb&amp;SP=EC&amp;rID=3462147&amp;rKey=ee4363ea3e092965 \" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">click here</a> to view the webinar recording.</p>",
