        seoTitle:
            "“PPS Final Rule 2011: What Will It Mean for You?” Free Webinar",
        seoDescription:
            "Learn how the PPS Final Rule for 2011 impacts home care providers through this informative webinar.",
        html: "<p>As you likely know, CMS has released the <a title=\"Final Rule for 2011\" href=\"https://www.cms.gov/HomeHealthPPS/HHPPSRN/itemdetail.asp?filterType=none&amp;filterByDID=0&amp;sortByDID=3&amp;sortOrder=ascending&amp;itemID=CMS1240989&amp;intNumPerPage=10\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Final Rule for 2011</a> and it contained some significant changes for the home care industry in the upcoming year.&nbsp; We know that many of you may have questions or concerns about what these changes may mean to you.&nbsp; Because of this, we are offering a <strong>free</strong> webinar on December 7<sup>th</sup> that will address the upcoming changes and how they will affect home care agencies.<img src=\"http://www.cernahealth.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-o-matic/cache/e5371_1240163650550219484Anonymous_Computer.svg.med1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"PPS Final Rule 2011\" width=\"150\" height=\"128\" class=\"alignRight\" style=\"float: right;\" /></p>\n<p>The webinar will be presented by Cheri Whalen, HEALTHCARE<em>first</em>'s Vice President of EDI and Regulatory.&nbsp; Cheri has over 17 years of Home Health and Hospice experience and has helped HEALTHCARE<em>first</em> customers navigate regulatory changes for over seven years.</p>\n<p><strong><em>This webinar, \"PPS Final Rule 2011: What Will it Mean for You?\" is offered to you <span>free of charge</span>! It will be held on December 7th at 10:30 am CT.</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong><em><a title=\"Click here to register!\" href=\"https://healthcarefirstevents.webex.com/healthcarefirstevents/onstage/g.php?t=a&amp;d=662301529\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Click here to register!</a><br /></em></strong></p>",
